<subSubSection id="C3496516FFD4D113FF3FFBCFFDB4031D" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BEC369DFFD4D113FF3FFBCFFDB4031D" blockId="6.[151,1436,974,1287]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">
While all possible care was exercised during preparation of my article on 
<collectingCountry id="F344760DFFD4D113FBFEFBCFFBF1026C" box="[1030,1100,1118,1143]" name="Israel" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">Israeli</collectingCountry>
<taxonomicName id="4C534D1EFFD4D113FBABFBCEFA25026C" authority="Mostovski, 2016" authorityName="Mostovski" authorityYear="2016" box="[1107,1432,1118,1143]" class="Insecta" family="Phoridae" genus="Metopina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B927EA8FFFD4D113FBABFBCEFB02026D" box="[1107,1215,1119,1142]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">Metopina</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFC24B6CFFD4D113FB35FBCFFA2D026C" author="Mostovski" box="[1229,1424,1118,1143]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" refString="Mostovski, M. (2016) Metopina Macquart (Diptera: Phoridae) of Israel, with description of a new species, new records and an identification key. Zootaxa, 4111 (1), 61 - 68. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4111.1.5" type="journal article" year="2016">
Mostovski, 
<number id="3D9B24BAFFD4D113FAACFBCFFA2D026C" box="[1364,1424,1118,1143]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" value="2016.0">2016</number>
</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, an embarrassing error crept in inadvertently in the spelling of 
<taxonomicName id="4C534D1EFFD4D113FCA6FB15FB9A0280" box="[862,1063,1154,1179]" class="Insecta" family="Phoridae" genus="Metopina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="braueri">
<emphasis id="B927EA8FFFD4D113FCA6FB15FB9A0280" box="[862,1063,1154,1179]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">Metopina braueri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which inexplicably appeared as ‘ 
<taxonomicName id="4C534D1EFFD4D113FF58FB37FF5B02A4" authority="Walker, 1850" authorityName="Walker" authorityYear="1850" box="[160,230,1190,1215]" class="Insecta" family="Tabanidae" genus="Phara" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B927EA8FFFD4D113FF58FB37FF5B02A4" box="[160,230,1190,1215]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">Phara</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
’ 
<taxonomicName id="4C534D1EFFD4D113FF0EFB37FEF702A4" box="[246,330,1190,1215]" class="Insecta" family="Phoridae" genus="Metopina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="braueri">
<emphasis id="B927EA8FFFD4D113FF0EFB37FEF702A4" box="[246,330,1190,1215]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">braueri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
on page 
<number id="3D9B24BAFFD4D113FE48FB37FE7102A4" box="[432,460,1190,1215]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" value="62.0">62</number>
of the paper. (The valid name 
<taxonomicName id="4C534D1EFFD4D113FCDBFB37FBB802A4" authority="Walker, 1850" authorityName="Walker" authorityYear="1850" box="[803,1029,1190,1215]" class="Insecta" family="Tabanidae" genus="Phara" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B927EA8FFFD4D113FCDBFB37FCD402A4" box="[803,873,1190,1215]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">Phara</emphasis>
Walker, 
<number id="3D9B24BAFFD4D113FC35FB37FBB802A4" box="[973,1029,1190,1215]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" value="1850.0">1850</number>
</taxonomicName>
refers to a subgenus of the horse fly genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C534D1EFFD4D113FF27FB5BFD9402F8" authority="Wiedemann, 1828" authorityName="Wiedemann" authorityYear="1828" box="[223,553,1226,1251]" class="Insecta" family="Tabanidae" genus="Philoliche" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B927EA8FFFD4D113FF27FB5BFEEE02F8" box="[223,339,1226,1251]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">Philoliche</emphasis>
Wiedemann, 
<number id="3D9B24BAFFD4D113FE16FB5AFD9402F8" box="[494,553,1227,1251]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" value="1828.0">1828</number>
</taxonomicName>
. There is also an invalid name 
<taxonomicName id="4C534D1EFFD4D113FC7DFB5BFBD502F8" authority="Walker, 1854" authorityName="Walker" authorityYear="1854" box="[901,1128,1226,1251]" class="Insecta" family="Tabanidae" genus="Phara" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B927EA8FFFD4D113FC7DFB5BFC7602F8" box="[901,971,1226,1251]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">Phara</emphasis>
Walker, 
<quantity id="4CAB9B78FFD4D113FBC8FB5BFBD502F8" box="[1072,1128,1226,1251]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.70916" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" unit="in" value="1854.0">1854</quantity>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<taxonomicName id="4C534D1EFFD4D113FB74FB5BFB4402F8" box="[1164,1273,1226,1251]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Arctiidae</taxonomicName>
.) This mistake must be treated as 
<emphasis id="B927EA8FFFD4D113FE9FFB7FFDBF031C" box="[359,514,1262,1287]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="67">lapsus calami</emphasis>
.
</paragraph>
